
_________________________________________________________

			HELP
_________________________________________________________

Global commands
	+rules - Displays a listing of the hub rules.
	+faq - Displays a list of helpful links if you are having trouble.
	+motd - Displays the Message of the Day.
	+help - Displays a list of all commands available to you.
	+myinfo - Displays a your information.
	+reglist - Displays a list of registered users.
	+banlist - Displays a list of banned users.
	+hubinfo - Displays a information of the hub.
	+passwd - Change a your login password. (+passwd <Password>)
	+regme - Ask for registration on the hub.

OPs commands
	+regnew - Register a new user. Example (+regnew <Nick> <Class>)
	+regdel - Remove a user from reglist. Example (+regdel <Nick>)
	+permban - Ban a user. Example (+permban <Nick>)
	+bandel - Remove a user from banlist. Example (+bandel <Nick>)
	+hubmaxusers - Change a number of max. users (+hubmaxusers <Number>)
	+hubname - Change a name of the hub. Example (+hubname <Name>)
	+hubdesc - Change a description of the hub. Example (+hubdesc <Desc.>)
	+redirect - Redirect a user. (+redirect <Nick>/all <Address>)
	+reload - Reload a files with text.
	+kick - Kick a user. (+kick <Nick>)
	+banner - Displays a banner of the hub.
	+hublist - Add hub to a hublist.
	+getinfo - Displays a info of user. (+getinfo <Nick>)
	+mass - Displays a message on PM. (+mass text)
	+search - Change a search function. (+search <1/0>)

Owner commands
	+shutdown - Shutdown a hub.
	+restart - Restart a hub.
